  "title": "FINANCIAL CONSULTANT",
  "description": "<p>Join one of Singapore’s most dynamic investment firms as it expands its exclusive private client division, in partnership with global investment leaders <strong>BlackRock</strong>, <strong>Fidelity</strong>, and <strong>Schroders</strong>. Backed by a strong private equity heritage, the firm delivers institutional-grade strategies to high-net-worth and ultra-high-net-worth clients seeking access to opportunities typically reserved for large institutions. This position offers a rare platform to craft sophisticated investment solutions, foster enduring client relationships, and contribute to a fast-growing firm redefining wealth management in Asia.<br /></p><p><strong>Preferred</strong></p><ul><li>Recent graduates, Financial Advisors, Relationship Managers, Private Bankers welcomed.</li><li>A background in investment analysis, portfolio management, or a related field in a private bank, asset management firm, or multi-family office.</li><li>Demonstrable experience in constructing and managing multi-asset class portfolios, with exposure to equities, fixed income, and alternative investments.</li><li>Practical experience in interpreting and applying institutional-grade investment research from leading global asset managers to inform strategy.</li><li>Experience within private banking or wealth management, with a verifiable track record of managing and growing a portfolio of HNW/UHNW relationships. The role is further supported by a consistent stream of qualified leads from the firm's established corporate partnerships.</li><li>A background that demonstrates exceptional interpersonal skills and the professional gravitas required to build rapport with entrepreneurs, C-suite executives, and multi-generational families.</li><li>A proven ability to deliver a superior service experience, with outstanding communication skills and a meticulous attention to client service detail.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Required</strong></p><ul><li>Will need to obtain or posses minimum 4 MAS papers</li><li>Singaporean Permanent Resident or Citizen only</li></ul><p><br />Send your CV to: 𝗽𝗵𝗶𝗹𝗶𝗽@𝘃𝗮𝗻𝗴𝘂𝗮𝗿𝗱𝗿𝗲𝗰𝗿𝘂𝗶𝘁𝗺𝗲𝗻𝘁.𝗰𝗼𝗺.𝘀𝗴<br />WhatsApp: <a href=\"https://wa.me/6584520693\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://wa.me/6584520693</a></p>",
